- form_for @book do |f|
  = f.hidden_field :title, :size => 40
  = f.hidden_field :subtitle, :size => 60
  = f.hidden_field :author, :size => 80
  = f.hidden_field(:email, :size => 60)
  = f.hidden_field(:password)
  .page.title
    It begins as follows…
    = f.text_area  :text
    %p Beautiful. This is just the beginning, you can continue writing after
    = f.submit 'having your new book saved'
  .shadow